%N A394385 Triangle read by rows: T(n,k) is the number of ordered rooted trees with node weights summing to n that have k leaf nodes; where the root has weight 0 and non-root nodes have positive integer weights.
%F A394385 G.f.: (1 - x*y + (x - 1)*sqrt((x^2*(y^2 + 4) - 2*x*(y + 2) + 1)/(x - 1)^2))/(2*x).
